text: Agdistis huemeri is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Iran and Turkmenistan (Kopet Dag).A new species, a new synonym, and new distribution records in the genus Agdistis Hübner, 1825 from Iran (Pterophoridae: Agdistinae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths of the Middle East Category:Moths described in 2002
title: Agdistis huemeri
